	<pre class="code-block"><code>[Brand]: Thanks for signing up. We will send updates and offers by text. Msg freq varies. Reply STOP to cancel, HELP for help.</code></pre>

	<h3>Lead follow-up</h3>
	<pre class="code-block"><code>[Brand]: Thanks for reaching out. Here is the next step: [branded link]. Questions? Reply here or call [phone]. Reply STOP to cancel.</code></pre>

	<h3>Appointment reminder</h3>
	<pre class="code-block"><code>[Brand]: Reminder: your appointment is [date] at [time]. Need to reschedule? Visit [branded link] or call [phone]. Reply STOP to cancel.</code></pre>

